      <title>我改变主意了。美联储现在需要降息。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/i-changed-my-mind-the-fed-needs-to-cut-rates-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社观点专栏作家比尔·杜德利改变了主意。美联储需要立即降息。等到 9 月会不必要地增加经济衰退的风险。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/i-changed-my-mind-the-fed-needs-to-cut-rates-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 16:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
