      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 16:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通就沃尔格林垃圾债券的潜在前景向投资者发出邀请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/jpmorgan-sounds-out-investors-on-potential-walgreens-junk-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，摩根大通公司正在就沃尔格林联合博姿公司 (Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc.) 可能出售高收益债券一事向投资者试探，以解决这家最近被下调评级的连锁药店的近期债务到期问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/jpmorgan-sounds-out-investors-on-potential-walgreens-junk-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 16:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TotalEnergies 首席执行官表示纽约上市计划正在取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-ceo-says-plan-for-new-york-listing-is-progressing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TotalEnergies SE 首席执行官 Patrick Pouyanne 表示，这家法国能源巨头正在推进在纽约上市的计划，以吸引更多美国投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-ceo-says-plan-for-new-york-listing-is-progressing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:58:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>皇家加勒比邮轮因经济放缓担忧导致股息重启黯淡而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/royal-caribbean-restarts-dividends-after-four-year-hiatus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皇家加勒比游轮有限公司 (Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd.) 股价下跌，因为投资者忽视了该公司恢复分红，而是关注该游轮公司快速增长放缓的可能信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/royal-caribbean-restarts-dividends-after-four-year-hiatus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:36:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场股市因中国措施不力跌至五周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/emerging-market-stocks-hit-5-week-low-as-china-steps-fall-short</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股票周四跌至五周以来的最低点，因为中国本周第二次放松货币政策未能缓解人们对该国经济放缓的担忧。全球对人工智能的担忧加剧了人们的悲观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/emerging-market-stocks-hit-5-week-low-as-china-steps-fall-short</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 10:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
